### Amount Styling Functions

**getAmountColor**:
```typescript
export function getAmountColor(
  type: 'deposit' | 'withdrawal' | 'interest'
): string {
  switch (type) {
    case 'deposit':
    case 'interest':
      return 'text-green-600'
    case 'withdrawal':
      return 'text-red-600'
  }
}
```

**getAmountPrefix**:
```typescript
export function getAmountPrefix(
  type: 'deposit' | 'withdrawal' | 'interest'
): string {
  switch (type) {
    case 'deposit':
    case 'interest':
      return '+'
    case 'withdrawal':
      return '-'
  }
}
```

**Usage**:
```typescript
<span className={getAmountColor(transaction.type)}>
  {getAmountPrefix(transaction.type)}{amount}
</span>
```

**Benefits**: Consistent styling across all amount displays

